OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA grey and murky start this
OL,6,Fmorning, with some coastal fog in the
OL,7,Fwest. Cloud will gradually break up in
OL,8,Fthe east leading to some sunshine
OL,9,Fhere, but staying rather cloudy
OL,10,Ffurther west. Feeling very warm and
OL,11,Fhumid.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FSome late sunshine in the
OL,14,Feast, otherwise a rather cloudy night
OL,15,Fwith some outbreaks of rain and
OL,16,Fdrizzle spreading east. Remaining
OL,17,Fhumid, with some murky conditions near
OL,18,Fcoasts.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
